    "name": "BPAQ-SF 攻击性问卷简版",
    "fullName": "Buss-Perry Aggression Questionnaire Short Form",
    "description": "BPAQ-SF 是一份包含 12 个条目的自评量表，用于评估攻击性的四个维度：身体攻击、言语攻击、愤怒和敌意。它是 BPAQ-29 的简版，简洁高效，适用于快速筛查攻击性水平。",
    "author": "Bryant & Smith (2001)",
    "license": "Free for research use",
    "reference": "Bryant FB, Smith BD. Refining the architecture of aggression: a measurement model for the Buss-Perry Aggression Questionnaire. J Res Pers. 2001;35(2):138-167.",
    "instruction": "请根据你的日常行为和感受选择最符合的选项。",
    "population": "成人（18岁以上）"
  },
